Carnival Eats - Season 2, Episode 6




From Chowchilla-Madera to Ciao!

In the tiny town of Chowchilla, CA Noah Cappe discovers some carnival eats that deserve to be shared with the world. Across the country in New Jersey, the St. Michael's Italian Festival celebrates the cultural and culinary history of Italian-Americans.




Original Air Date: 20-Aug-2015
